{"tid":1088930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳冠希拖女兒遊日被追拍扯火 網民鬧拍片者不對","createTime":"2019-04-02T11:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T04:34:41.000Z","uid":16343,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"f4bb9bb638c19b92ea982d9cdda6ad35d42e3259","tid":1088930,"uid":16343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T11:48:25.000Z","msg":"陳冠希（Edison）前年3月榮升爸爸後，經常在網上晒她和女兒Alaia，還有超模女友秦舒培的幸福家庭照，不少人都認為Edison雖然性格向來火爆，但自囡囡出生後都改變了不少，而且當她看見女兒時，笑容更加充滿愛，百分百是個慈父。<br />\n<br />\n不過，繼早前Edison不滿在機場被偷拍，掃低拍片者手機後，昨日有大陸Blogger上載一條在日本街頭遇上Edison拖着囡囡的影片，指自己本來想邀Edison影相，但對方卻發怒，可是今次拍片者未被網友支持，反而指他不對，不少人留言都撐Edison「明顯是主播的問題，人家已經講了不行」、「當第一次人家禮貌回絕的時候，這主播就應該收手了」、「主播是感覺遇到紅一波的機會了吧」。<br />\n<br />\nBlogger沒有說明影片是何時拍，但片段一開始，他已用鏡頭對準正拖着囡囡過馬路的Edison，然後一邊說：「是陳冠希老師吧！」之後他便向Edison表示想影合照，當時拖着Alaia的Edison就禮貌回應他，並指一指身邊的囡囡說：「跟小孩子一齊啊！今天不好意思呀！」可是拍片者一直跟着他，最終「成功」把Edison激嬲，之後還在旁述:「我全家都在這邊，你這樣不太好吧」、「這裡有十萬人在看」，極度容易「扯火」的Edison便回應他說:「我的微博有三千萬人呀！你想怎麼樣啊，你還跟著我。」<br />\n<br />\n影片曝光後，即時引來網民熱議，惟Edison今次獲大比數網民支持，不少人看過影片後都認為是Blogger不對，事關影片一開始，指Edison本來好有禮貌，是拍片故意令他發嬲。所以，下次把影片放上網前，還是先自我審查一下比較好，否則只會得到反效果，輸得好慘烈！<br />\n杜汶澤在facebook留言支持Edison：「聽到拍片嗰個人把聲，又無賴又賤，你就知道，其實陳冠希已經幾好老脾&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190402/59440501?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_content=share_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190402%2F59440501%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&d=mFE05qKCD2WHpL72sA8m6426uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=15ddb2a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190402%2F59440501%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&h=ab023fcb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190402/59440501?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_content=share_link</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次撐冠希啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a90124ed48e98172e1d8fb6250e5ff39e6a44f9","tid":1088930,"uid":14625,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T11:51:59.000Z","msg":"「這裡有十萬人在看」，極度容易「扯火」的Edison便回應他說:「我的微博有三千萬人呀！你想怎麼樣啊，你還跟著我。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f5bdaad54c14bbbbded283edaf88d147e99207","tid":1088930,"uid":34313,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4a90124ed48e98172e1d8fb6250e5ff39e6a44f9","tid":1088930,"uid":14625,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T11:51:59.000Z","msg":"「這裡有十萬人在看」，極度容易「扯火」的Edison便回應他說:「我的微博有三千萬人呀！你想怎麼樣啊，你還跟著我。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T11:59:40.000Z","msg":"一句KO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84e2d5aa63fd8ca49181b51798cd5b4a94d4284","tid":1088930,"uid":17426,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T12:03:12.000Z","msg":"同大陸人講文明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3612672f0dd221554f016e144d6de7fff15c4ad8","tid":1088930,"uid":5166,"like":19,"dislike":7,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T12:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QVcnXNP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQVcnXNP.gif&h=9bdc19fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ec9be715bbfb1a76bca65ebf7d1bea64a60f012","tid":1088930,"uid":4917,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T12:05:19.000Z","msg":"陳冠希響支那變左做支那人嘅玩具，以激嬲佢為樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\